nservice-1", "recommendationservice-2", "redis-cart-0", "shippingservice-0", "shippingservice-1", "shippingservice-2"], "metric_name": ["client_error_ratio", "duration_99th", "error_ratio", "failed_query_ops", "memory_usage", "pod_cpu_usage", "rrt", "rrt_max", "server_error_ratio", "store_unhealth_count"]}, "node_pod_mapping": {"aiops-k8s-01": ["emailservice-1", "productcatalogservice-2", "recommendationservice-2", "shippingservice-0", "checkoutservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-02": [], "aiops-k8s-03": ["recommendationservice-1", "adservice-0", "shippingservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-04": ["currencyservice-0", "checkoutservice-0", "paymentservice-2", "frontend-0", "cartservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-05": ["checkoutservice-2", "paymentservice-1", "cartservice-1", "checkoutservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["productcatalogservice-1", "frontend-1", "emailservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["shippingservice-1", "emailservice-0", "currencyservice-1", "cartservice-0", "adservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["currencyservice-2", "checkoutservice-1", "cartservice-2", "adservice-2", "paymentservice-0", "redis-cart-0", "recommendationservice-0", "productcatalogservice-0", "frontend-2"]}, "matched_anomaly": "The system experienced an anomaly from 2025-06-21T13:10:29Z to 2025-06-21T13:21:29Z. Please infer the possible cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-21 13:10:29+00:00 to 2025-06-21 13:21:29+00:00"}, "metric_data_collected": true, "node_pod_mapping": {"aiops-k8s-01": ["emailservice-1", "productcatalogservice-2", "recommendationservice-2", "shippingservice-0", "checkoutservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-02": [], "aiops-k8s-03": ["recommendationservice-1", "adservice-0", "shippingservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-04": ["currencyservice-0", "checkoutservice-0", "paymentservice-2", "frontend-0", "cartservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-05": ["checkoutservice-2", "paymentservice-1", "cartservice-1", "checkoutservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["productcatalogservice-1", "frontend-1", "emailservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["shippingservice-1", "emailservice-0", "currencyservice-1", "cartservice-0", "adservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["currencyservice-2", "checkoutservice-1", "cartservice-2", "adservice-2", "paymentservice-0", "redis-cart-0", "recommendationservice-0", "productcatalogservice-0", "frontend-2"]}, "available_metric_names": ["client_error_ratio", "duration_99th", "error_ratio", "failed_query_ops", "memory_usage", "pod_cpu_usage", "rrt", "rrt_max", "server_error_ratio", "store_unhealth_count"], "log_analysis_findings": "基于对异常时间段内日志数据的分析，我已经识别出了关键的错误模式和根因。以下是详细分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"Error 9005 (HY000)\", \"Region is unavailable\", \"rpc error\", \"context canceled\", \"productcatalogservice--database\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"数据库Region不可用导致的产品目录服务故障 (Error 9005: Region is unavailable)\",\n      \"evidence\": \"productcatalogservice日志显示: 'failed to query product by id: Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable' (出现235次)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"由于productcatalogservice数据库故障导致的级联错误 (rpc error: Error 9005)\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend日志显示: 'could not retrieve product: rpc error: code = Unknown desc = Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable' (高频出现)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"数据库连接超时导致的上下文取消错误 (context canceled)\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend日志显示: 'could not retrieve currencies: rpc error: code = Canceled desc = context canceled'\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 分析总结\n\n**主要故障模式**：\n1. **根因服务**: `productcatalogservice` 的数据库出现Region不可用错误 (Error 9005)\n2. **影响范围**: 所有frontend服务无法获取产品信息，导致用户请求失败\n3. **故障特征**: 数据库Region级别的可用性问题，影响整个产品目录查询功能\n\n**关键发现**：\n- productcatalogservice-0实例出现235次数据库错误，是主要故障源\n- 所有frontend实例都受到此故障影响，出现大量RPC调用失败\n- 故障时间与异常时间段完全吻合，表明这是系统级联故障的根本原因", "trace_analysis_findings": "基于对调用链数据的全面扫描分析，我发现了以下显著异常模式。以下是初始扫描阶段的发现：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"frontend->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"productcatalogservice->tidb\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"ProductCatalogService的GetProduct接口延迟从正常约10秒激增至3800万秒（约44天），延迟倍数高达3800倍以上\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\", \n      \"evidence\": \"所有ProductCatalogService调用都返回错误状态码2，错误消息为'Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable'\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"TiDB数据库\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"错误消息显示Region不可用，表明底层TiDB数据库出现严重问题，导致ProductCatalogService无法正常访问数据\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Frontend服务接收HTTP请求返回500错误，出现次数达100次，是ProductCatalogService故障的传播结果\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"CheckoutService的PlaceOrder操作失败，错误信息显示无法获取产品信息，是ProductCatalogService故障的连锁反应\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**关键发现总结：**\n\n1. **根因定位**：ProductCatalogService是问题的源头，所有异常都源于该服务对TiDB数据库的访问失败。\n\n2. **错误类型**：明确的数据库连接问题 - \"Region is unavailable\"错误表明TiDB数据库的某个region不可用。\n\n3. **影响范围**：\n   - 直接影响：所有依赖ProductCatalogService的服务（Frontend、CheckoutService、RecommendationService）\n   - 间接影响：整个系统的商品相关功能完全瘫痪\n\n4. **异常特征**：极端的延迟增加（3800倍）结合100%的错误率，表明是数据库层面的严重故障。", "metric_analysis_findings": "基于对异常时间段（2025-06-21T13:10:29Z 至 2025-06-21T13:21:29Z）的指标数据分析，我发现了多个显著的异常模式。以下是分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"rrt\", \"rrt_max\", \"error_ratio\", \"client_error_ratio\", \"server_error_ratio\", \"duration_99th\", \"failed_query_ops\", \"memory_usage\", \"pod_cpu_usage\", \"store_unhealth_count\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"严重的响应时间异常和错误率上升，rrt从5ms激增至20s，rrt_max达到40s，表明服务性能严重退化\",\n      \"evidence\": \"productcatalogservice-1: rrt从5ms升至20s (变化率1.999)，rrt_max从23ms升至40s (变化率1.9977)；所有实例均出现类似问题\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"前端服务响应时间急剧增加和错误率上升，rrt从8ms升至17-20s，server_error_ratio达20-25%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend-0: rrt从8.6ms升至17.3s (变化率1.998)，error_ratio从0%升至21.57%；frontend-1和frontend-2也出现类似异常\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"tidb-tidb\",\n      \"reason\": \"数据库性能严重下降，duration_99th从10ms激增至65s，failed_query_ops出现异常峰值\",\n      \"evidence\": \"tidb-tidb: duration_99th从10ms升至65s (变化率1.9994)，failed_query_ops p99值达到61.33，内存使用率下降66%可能表明重启\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"错误率显著上升，特别是shippingservice-2的error_ratio和client_error_ratio达到50%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"shippingservice-2: error_ratio从0%升至50%，client_error_ratio同样从0%升至50%；其他实例p99错误率也显著上升\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"tidb-pd\",\n      \"reason\": \"存储健康状态异常，store_unhealth_count p99值出现0.9的非零值\",\n      \"evidence\": \"tidb-pd: store_unhealth_count p99从0升至0.9，表明TiDB集群存储节点健康状态出现问题\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**关键发现总结**：\n1. **数据库性能瓶颈**：TiDB数据库出现严重的响应时间退化（65秒延迟）和查询失败\n2. **服务级联故障**：productcatalogservice的性能问题直接影响了依赖它的frontend服务\n3. **错误率上升**：多个服务出现错误率异常，特别是shippingservice和frontend\n4. **存储健康问题**：TiDB集群出现存储节点健康状态异常\n\n最可能的根因是**TiDB数据库性能问题**，这导致了依赖数据库服务的应用级联故障。"}
